to be considered armed and extremely dangerous.

79
00:06:00,226 --> 00:06:01,928
I don't get it.

80
00:06:01,994 --> 00:06:03,730
Come on, Thorold.

81
00:06:03,796 --> 00:06:05,998
They've seen the same thing as the rest of us.

82
00:06:06,065 --> 00:06:08,935
Every nuclear weapon on earth gone.

83
00:06:09,001 --> 00:06:11,571
Millions of people vanishing into thin air.

84
