you never believed in anything. At every puppet show,

91
00:06:31,124 --> 00:06:34,026
you're looking for strings. At Christmas,

92
00:06:34,093 --> 00:06:37,630
you're looking for Santa's footprints on the roof. Finally

93
00:06:37,697 --> 00:06:40,800
you got all the proof you need, and it's still not good enough!

94
00:06:40,867 --> 00:06:43,636
Maybe I'm not looking for God.

95
00:06:43,703 --> 00:06:46,939
I'm just looking for my family.

96
00:06:48,107 --> 00:06:51,477
Orders are to terminate. No prisoners, no dialogue.

97
00:07:11,864 --> 00:07:13,166
(device beeping)

98
