Claims this thing can read human D.N.A. through solid concrete.

102
00:07:22,141 --> 00:07:25,745
And sure enough, there's a bunch of them down at the far end.

103
00:07:37,256 --> 00:07:40,059
(truck rumbling to a stop)

104
00:07:47,767 --> 00:07:49,635
All right, I know you heard the order to shoot these

105
00:07:49,702 --> 00:07:52,972
people on sight, but listen up. Nobody fires a single shot

106
00:07:53,039 --> 00:07:56,676
unless they get the word from me, you got that?

107
00:07:56,742 --> 00:07:58,110
Yeah, I got it.

108
00:07:58,177 --> 00:08:00,613
Let's go.

109
