(clapping, cheers)

118
00:08:46,893 --> 00:08:50,630
Amen, Amen, Amen Hallelujah.

119
00:08:50,696 --> 00:08:52,632
Why are you glad, friends?

120
00:08:52,698 --> 00:08:56,903
One reason. One reason: the truth.

121
00:08:56,969 --> 00:09:03,042
Yeah, Praise god and then blow up the buses, huh? Nice touch.

122
00:09:03,109 --> 00:09:05,711
Well, it's not the first time something was

123
00:09:05,778 --> 00:09:08,281
blown up in the name of the Almighty.

124
00:09:08,347 --> 00:09:10,816
Satan cannot win!

125
00:09:10,883 --> 00:09:12,084
Hallelujah!

126
00:09:12,151 --> 00:09:13,119
Amen...

127
00:09:13,185 --> 00:09:14,520
Hallelujah!

128
00:09:14,587 --> 00:09:16,055
And that's why they're trying to exterminate us.

129
00:09:16,122 --> 00:09:20,660
Your job is to keep the faith, and to spread the truth

130
00:09:20,726 --> 00:09:26,265
to whoever will listen. But I warn you, it won't be easy.

131
00:09:26,332 --> 00:09:30,336
No sir, it won't be easy. Because they've all seen

132
00:09:30,403 --> 00:09:35,441
Macalusso's miracles, well, I'm here to tell you today

133
00:09:35,508 --> 00:09:40,146
that in God's world, seeing is not believing. No, sir!

134
00:09:40,212 --> 00:09:42,882
That's satan's way of trickery.

135
00:09:42,949 --> 00:09:47,853
In God's world, you must first believe it before you see it.

136
00:09:47,920 --> 00:09:50,022
All right, here's the deal.

137
00:09:50,089 --> 00:09:52,425
We're gonna load 'em all into the truck

138
00:09:52,491 --> 00:09:54,393
