139
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:55,828
Whattya mean, take 'em down for questioning?

140
00:09:55,895 --> 00:09:57,096
Our orders are to shoot--

141
00:09:57,163 --> 00:09:58,097
We're takin' 'em down to headquarters!

142
00:09:58,164 --> 00:09:59,632
Back off.

143
00:09:59,699 --> 00:10:04,236
...that is why the bible says that only, only as a child

144
00:10:04,303 --> 00:10:07,273
will you enter through the gates of heaven.

145
00:10:07,340 --> 00:10:08,474
Hallelujah.

146
00:10:08,541 --> 00:10:09,942
Hallelujah!

147
00:10:10,009 --> 00:10:13,946
Do you know what that means? Do you know what that means?

148
00:10:14,013 --> 00:10:15,081
I'll tell you what it means!

149
00:10:15,147 --> 00:10:16,015
Go!

150
00:10:16,082 --> 00:10:18,250
Get 'em up, now! Get 'em up, now!

151
00:10:18,317 --> 00:10:19,452
You're all under arrest! Get your hands up!

152
00:10:19,518 --> 00:10:21,120
Get up!

153
00:10:21,187 --> 00:10:22,054
Get 'em up!

154
00:10:22,121 --> 00:10:23,055
Get back!

155
00:10:23,122 --> 00:10:24,423
We didn't do anything!

156
00:10:24,490 --> 00:10:25,891
Yeah, back off, lady!

157
00:10:25,958 --> 00:10:27,360
If it wasn't for him, you'd all be dead right now.

158
00:10:27,426 --> 00:10:29,695
'Cause if it was up to me, I'd shoot every one of you.

159
00:10:31,163 --> 00:10:32,865
Nothing. Not even a knife.

160
00:10:32,932 --> 00:10:35,835
What do you expect? We're not criminals!

161
00:10:35,901 --> 00:10:41,107
Not until worshipping the true and living God became a crime, that is.

162
00:10:41,173 --> 00:10:42,908
Well, if the God you're worshipping is so full of hate,

163
00:10:42,975 --> 00:10:45,144
he's got you blowin' up school buses, then maybe

164
00:10:45,211 --> 00:10:47,880
it's time to re-examine your faith, preacher.

165
00:10:47,947 --> 00:10:49,281
Load 'em up.

166
00:10:49,348 --> 00:10:52,284
Time to get off the soapbox. Let's go, go now!

167
00:10:52,351 --> 00:10:56,756
We didn't blow up anything! Can't you see we're bein' set up?

168
00:10:56,822 --> 00:10:57,890
Don't waste your time--

169
00:10:57,957 --> 00:11:00,893
Hold on a second. Set up by who?

170
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,828
Franco Macalusso.

171
00:11:02,895 --> 00:11:05,131
And all his disciples who believe he's God.

172
00:11:05,197 --> 00:11:08,267
And let me guess, you really believe he's the devil, right?

173
00:11:08,334 --> 00:11:11,771
I guess he'd have to have horns and a red pointy tail for you to see it.

174
00:11:11,837 --> 00:11:13,773
The bible makes it perfectly clear!

175
00:11:13,839 --> 00:11:17,309
See Thorold, the same thing your wife was talkin' about.

176
00:11:17,376 --> 00:11:19,311
And you know where that got her?

177
00:11:19,378 --> 00:11:21,380
Gone, just like the rest of them!

178
00:11:21,447 --> 00:11:23,883
It got her to heaven, young man.

179
00:11:23,949 --> 00:11:26,552
I only wish we all could've seen the light before that day.

180
00:11:26,619 --> 00:11:32,992
We are all guilty of believin' the same thing your wife believed.

181
00:11:33,059 --> 00:11:35,461
I've heard enough, man. You deal with this.

182
00:11:35,528 --> 00:11:38,330
Let me ask you somethin'.

183
00:11:38,397 --> 00:11:40,466
Do you think your wife would be killin' children if she

184
00:11:40,533 --> 00:11:46,539
were still here? If you would just open your heart.

185
00:11:46,605 --> 00:11:49,241
Why didn't you let them shoot us?

186
00:11:49,308 --> 00:11:51,544
You don't look dangerous to me.

187
00:11:51,610 --> 00:11:57,049
If we're not dangerous, why do you think they want us dead?

188
00:11:57,116 --> 00:12:00,352
They believe you slaughtered innocent children.

189
00:12:00,419 --> 00:12:05,825
They know that's not true. They sent you here because of this.

190
00:12:05,891 --> 00:12:09,595
I worked for the O.N.E. until a couple days ago.

191
00:12:09,662 --> 00:12:12,898
I suggest you take a look at this.

192
00:12:12,965 --> 00:12:15,568
Do it for your wife.

193
00:12:15,634 --> 00:12:16,435
Let's go.

194
00:12:20,372 --> 00:12:22,908
Move it! Go!

195
00:12:24,043 --> 00:12:29,215
(alarm beeping)

196
00:12:30,082 --> 00:12:31,951
Oh, no. They got the Davis group.

197
00:12:32,017 --> 00:12:33,152
What about the CD?

198
00:12:33,219 --> 00:12:35,321
We'll have to assume they got that too.

199
00:12:35,387 --> 00:12:39,525
Poor Selma Davis. She was supposed to meet me here with it this afternoon.

200
00:12:39,592 --> 00:12:43,028
Oh well, that's just great! Now what?

201
00:12:43,095 --> 00:12:45,464
That CD was our only chance for seeing what the O.N.E.

202
00:12:45,531 --> 00:12:47,433
has planned for the Day of Wonders.

203
00:12:47,500 --> 00:12:49,568
It's okay, Jake. We'll just have to find another way.

204
00:12:49,635 --> 00:12:51,103
It's okay?

205
00:12:51,170 --> 00:12:53,405
We've been in this filthy dump for three months already.

206
00:12:53,472 --> 00:12:54,607
There's not a soul out there that wouldn't

207
00:12:54,673 --> 00:12:57,143
shred us to bits if they had the chance.

208
00:12:57,209 --> 00:12:59,211
I mean, for heaven's sake, the crowds cheered

209
00:12:59,278 --> 00:13:03,349
when they strung your boyfriend up on national television.

210
00:13:03,415 --> 00:13:04,884
I don't think that "okay" actually describes our situation!

211
00:13:04,950 --> 00:13:08,020
We can't blame them, Cindy. They don't know what we know.

212
00:13:08,087 --> 00:13:09,922
They also don't know that Macalusso's having

213
00:13:09,989 --> 00:13:12,124
everyone who disagrees with him killed.

214
00:13:12,191 --> 00:13:14,160
All they see are the miracles.

215
00:13:14,226 --> 00:13:16,195
Any luck, Ronnie?

216
00:13:16,262 --> 00:13:19,899
I'm all set up on the O.N.E. personnel file now. I'll be

217
00:13:19,965 --> 00:13:23,302
able to get in there tonight as a security guard. Without that

218
00:13:23,369 --> 00:13:27,006
disk, though, I don't have a clue what I'm lookin' for.

219
00:13:27,072 --> 00:13:29,575
Anything. Anything that can help us

220
00:13:29,642 --> 00:13:32,645
figure out what these guys have planned for the Day of Wonders.

221
00:13:32,711 --> 00:13:35,080
Because whatever they're planning, it's big.

222
00:13:35,147 --> 00:13:36,982
And it can't be good.

223
00:13:37,049 --> 00:13:38,984
Here, take a look at this. It's from a tape

224
00:13:39,051 --> 00:13:40,586
I found at my grandmother's house.

225
00:13:42,188 --> 00:13:46,091
We are living in the last days, friends.

226
00:13:46,158 --> 00:13:48,961
We know it because of all the prophecies that are being fulfilled.

227
00:13:49,028 --> 00:13:51,197
But it's going to get much worse.

228
00:13:51,263 --> 00:13:53,199
In fact, do you know that there will be a time

229
00:13:53,265 --> 00:13:57,570
when the devil rules over the entire earth?

230
00:13:57,636 --> 00:14:00,706
He will be a super-deceiver.

231
00:14:00,773 --> 00:14:04,076
And he'll try to let the world know that he is the promised

232
00:14:04,143 --> 00:14:08,214
Messiah, the Prince of Peace of Isaiah 9:6.

233
00:14:08,280 --> 00:14:10,382
And he will tell the world "I have come to save you

234
00:14:10,449 --> 00:14:14,053
from destruction", and they'll believe it because he confirms

235
00:14:14,119 --> 00:14:21,126
the peace pact for a period of seven years, in Daniel 9:27.

236
00:14:21,193 --> 00:14:24,630
But he's not the Messiah. He's an impostor.

237
00:14:24,697 --> 00:14:31,237
He is empowered and incarnated by Satan, Revelations 13:3.

238
00:14:31,303 --> 00:14:36,041
And therefore the peace pact fails.

239
00:14:36,108 --> 00:14:40,479
For the bible says "when they say 'peace and safety'

240
00:14:40,546 --> 00:14:45,284
then sudden destruction cometh upon them as a veil upon a

241
00:14:45,351 --> 00:14:49,922
woman with child, and they shall not escape".

242
00:14:50,589 --> 00:14:53,459
These people don't look any more dangerous than my wife and daughter did.

243
00:14:53,525 --> 00:14:55,628
Hey, I checked the satellite readout myself, okay?

244
00:14:55,694 --> 00:14:58,264
The command that detonated that bomb came from this very building.

245
00:14:58,330 --> 00:15:00,432
Well, maybe the detonator was on a timer, not the bomb.

246
00:15:00,499 --> 00:15:03,602
Maybe somebody just placed it here long before these people got here.

247
00:15:03,669 --> 00:15:06,672
No, no, that bomb went off exactly when the last kid got on that bus.

248
00:15:06,739 --> 00:15:09,375
Whoever set it off had their finger on the button.

249
00:15:09,441 --> 00:15:11,443
Wait a second, Niddy. You'd need some pretty sophisticated

250
00:15:11,510 --> 00:15:14,346
equipment to pull that off, and I didn't see anything in there like that.

251
00:15:14,413 --> 00:15:18,350
Okay, that's not our job. The bomb squad guys will find it.

252
00:15:18,417 --> 00:15:21,487
Maybe only one of them did it, and the rest of them are innocent.

253
00:15:21,553 --> 00:15:23,656
Yeah, and maybe the bomb was set off from a spaceship.

254
00:15:23,722 --> 00:15:27,293
Look, don't let what that lady in there said to you play with your mind, okay?

255
